item.title: CoD Warzone vs PUBG
item.description: For probably a good 2 years now I’ve been pretty much exclusively playing Playerunknown’s Battlegrounds (PUBG) on Xbox. I’ve played a lot of first/third person shooters over the years, but they’ve always felt really casual.
